    "These approaches can use as starting point automatic or manually labeled documents, and they learn how to create new layouts and contents which are reasonably similar to real ones.",
    "However, despite the recent improvement, creating synthetic documents is still a difficult task.",
    "Differently from manual and automatic procedures, in this case it is not possible to outline a general approach.",
    "Even if none of the datasets presented in this survey is generated, we found interesting to revise, to the best of our knowledge, the most important contributions developed so far in this direction.",
